Before any task in this repo, run the loop in docs/orchestration.md.

Read docs/brief.md, docs/hackathon.md, docs/architecture.md,
docs/design-system.md, docs/roadmap.md, and docs/resolution-log.md first. Build to those docs. Update them and append a
resolution log entry when you finish.

The docs/ set is the source of truth. This file only points there so every tool
starts in the same place.
